title: Learn Finnish While You Sleep: Housing in Finland

media:group.media:title: Learn Finnish While You Sleep: Housing in Finland
media:group.media:description:
Learn Finnish While You Sleep: housing in Finland 
Missä sinä asut? Where do you live
In this section we will talk about housing.we are going to learn about housing notices or housing advertising and what they mean.
First we will start with the types of Residence  (Asuminen) you can find in Finland and more importantly when searching for accommodation in Finland. then learn some housing terms used in housing adverts and notices.
